      "para_id": "Q004416.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Šu-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Lugal-amarkug , the scribe , child of Lugal-magure , the išib priest of Ninurta , is your servant ."
    }
  ],
